nodes.bodyText:
As stated in a prior review, these two checks should be swapped for performance reason.
Any BlockStorage operations might be heavy depending on their concurrent behaviour and take a relatively long time to compute, whereas the .isAir() check is very inexpensive.
Swapping will reduce those heavy lookups to a bare minimum.







